Functionality 

Team creation; add, remove and move members between teams

Employee creation; add, remove, edit. Needs name an position at creation 

Password protected application 

Encrypt stored information (If online)

Can enter a productive percentage (productive hours worked/ total hours worked) per team member which generates overall productive percentage per team 

Can enter profitability, value of a project, cost of project, funding spent as a percentage for a team 

Display all team performances over time as charts and graphs for the manager 

Ability to add new parameters to track 

Tracks engineer and customer satisfaction, track how proud engineers are of their project 

Team members can login and view anonymised comparison data e.g (see they are performing 52% more efficiently than 5 other engineers but not see which engineers) 
